Entries.default: "Back the way you came, if you know what's good for you."
"I'm a paying customer, I'll go where I please."
[Attack] "If you won't move, then you'll be dead."
"Master's orders. If you want to see more than what's been offered, you'll have to speak with Master Kua."
"Curiosity's killed more than a few runts like you."
"What... How did you..." She reaches for the horn on her side. "Sounding the horns, we have a trespasser!"
